What is D3?
	1. Library for rendering interactive visualizations in the browser
	2. A JS library capable of building interating visualization by manipualting the DOM
	3. A JS library  capable of building interactive visualizations by explicitly
		 binding data to html (dom) elements

What is a webpade
	1. structure - HTML(5)
	2. aestetics - CSS
	3. behaviors - JS

SVG - Scalable Vector Grapics
	1. Standard to Represent images in XML 
			- frequently embedded in HTML

Data Driven Docuemnts:
	- How does the data come into play?
		-> Explicitly map every element of the dataset into a DOM element <-


